pred_decomp = function(trainset, testset){
  n1 = length(trainset)
  n2 = length(testset)
  decomp = decompose(trainset)
  t = 1:n1
  t2 = t**2
  t3 = t**3
  reg_lin = lm(decomp$trend ~ t + t2 + t3)
  x = (n1 + 1) : (n1 + n2)
  x2 = x**2
  x3 = x**3
  trend = reg_lin$coefficients[1] + x * reg_lin$coefficients[2] + x2 * reg_lin$coefficients[3] + x3 * reg_lin$coefficients[4]
  if (n2%%7==0){
    print("ok")
    seasons = c(rep(decomp$figure, n2%/%7))
  }else{
    print(n2)
    print(n2%/%7)
    seasons = c(rep(decomp$figure, n2%/%7), decomp$figure[1:n2%%7])
  }
  trend + seasons
}

plot(pred_decomp(trainset, testset), type="l", ylab="PrÃ©diction")

getPerformance = function(pred, val) {
    res = pred - val
    MAE = sum(abs(res))/length(val)
    MAPE = sum(abs(res)/abs(val)*100)/length(val)
    RSS = sum(res^2)
    MSE = RSS/length(val)
    RMSE = sqrt(MSE)
    perf = data.frame(MAE, MAPE, RSS, MSE, RMSE)
}
models = c("decomp + SARIMA",

           "log + SARIMA (d=1, D=1)",
           "BoxCox + SARIMA (d=1, D=1)",
           "Box-CoxSARIMA (d=1, D=1)")
